OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWomen's safety: Police     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fvideo calls to verify Met  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fofficers                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Plain-clothes officers in London will  
OL,6, video call a uniformed colleague to    
OL,7, confirm their identity when stopping a 
OL,8, lone woman, it has been announced.     
OL,10,FDame Cressida Dick said the new system 
OL,11,Fwould be introduced after Sarah Everard
OL,12,Fwas murdered by a serving officer who  
OL,13,Ffaked an arrest in order to kidnap her.
OL,15,FShe told City Hall "the onus is on the 
OL,16,Fofficer" to make lone women feel safe. 
OL,18,FThe video call will be "instigated by  
OL,19,Fthe officer and not by the woman having
OL,20,Fto ask for this," Dame Cressida said.  
